.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
# Git worktrees live here (runtime scratch checkouts of other branches). Keep
# them out of git AND out of content scanners (Tailwind v4 auto-source detection
# respects .gitignore) — otherwise a worktree's duplicate src/site assets get
# scanned, and removing a worktree leaves dangling asset refs that 500 the dev
# server (e.g. ENOENT on a worktree's ridge-mark.svg from the CSS pipeline).
.claude/worktrees/
.aider*
scripts/perf-runs/
bash.exe.stackdump
.ridge-remote-port
/coverage
/test-results
/static/remote
/packages/ridge-term/pkg
plotforge.db

# Rust workspace build output. S1 (ridge-core extraction) added a virtual
# workspace root, relocating the cargo target dir from `src-tauri/target` to the
# repo root (`src-tauri/.gitignore` still covers the old path).
/target

# CDP dev-test artifacts
.cdp-shots/
.dev-cdp.log

# Playwright remote-GC e2e artifacts (throwaway)
.pw-remote-profile/
gc-e2e-*.png
